S5-T04: Integration tests for stats endpoints and security test cases.

Completed: 2026-04-05

Deliverables:
1. tests/integration/stats_test.go - 9 tests covering stats endpoints
   - TestGetLinkStats_ValidOwner, TestGetLinkStats_WrongOwner, TestGetLinkStats_Unauthenticated
   - TestGetLinkTimeline_HourGranularity, TestGetLinkTimeline_DayGranularity
   - TestGetLinkGeo_MultipleCountries, TestGetLinkReferrers_MultipleReferrers
   - TestGetLinkStats_NonexistentCode, TestGetLinkStats_ZeroClicks

2. tests/integration/auth_test.go - 7 tests covering auth middleware
   - TestAuthMiddleware_NoToken_AnonymousAccess, TestAuthMiddleware_ValidToken_SetsContext
   - TestAuthMiddleware_InvalidToken_Returns401, TestAuthMiddleware_ExpiredToken_Returns401
