3. tests/integration/security_test.go - 13 tests covering SEC-001 through SEC-010
   - SEC001: Private IP rejection (SSRF prevention)
   - SEC002: javascript:/data:/vbscript: scheme rejection
   - SEC003: Rate limit enforcement (429)
   - SEC004: XSS in title (stored safely as JSON)
   - SEC005: SQL injection in custom code
   - SEC006: Bcrypt password hashing verification
   - SEC007: CSRF stub verification
   - SEC008: Security headers / Content-Type enforcement
   - SEC009: Body size limit / field validation
   - SEC010: IP anonymization (SHA-256, no plaintext)
   - Cross-user resource access (delete, update, stats)
   - Invalid token format handling

4. tests/integration/helpers_test.go - Shared mocks and test setup
5. tests/integration/api_server_test.go - Integration API server (mirrors cmd/api/server.go)

All 29 tests pass with -race. BDD step definitions unchanged (pending stubs already reference correct Store methods).
